# Build context for apps/web/Dockerfile is `apps/` — it needs only `web/` and
# `turbomap/` (the WASM renderer, a file: dependency of the web app). Exclude the
# heavy siblings + all build artifacts so the context upload stays small.
# (This only applies when `apps/` itself is the build context; the other apps
# build from their own subdir, with their own .dockerignore.)
android/
ios/
flutter/
api/
tileserver/

# Build artifacts anywhere under the context.
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.gradle/
**/pkg/
**/.git/
